OL,3,CClaire's and The Original Factory Shop
OL,4,Ccollapse into administration
OL,6,FIt will mean 1,355 employees in the UK
OL,7,Fand Ireland at 154 Claire's shops will
OL,8,Fbe put at risk, and 1,220 staff across
OL,9,F140 TOFS' stores.
OL,11,FA spokesman for the company said: "We
OL,12,Fhave worked intensively in an effort
OL,13,Fto save both businesses, having made
OL,14,Flast-ditch attempts to rescue them,
OL,15,Fbut neither has a realistic
OL,16,Fpossibility of trading profitably
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,19,F"In these circumstances,
OL,20,Fadministration is the only option.
