OL,4,Ccollapse into administration
OL,6,F"In both cases, the legacy effects of
OL,7,Ftrading prior to our ownership left
OL,8,Fthem highly vulnerable."
OL,10,FModella said tough retail conditions,
OL,11,Fincluding those from government
OL,12,Fpolicies, were causing British
OL,13,Fbusinesses to "suffer".
OL,15,F"The climate on the high street
OL,16,Fremains extremely challenging, and
OL,17,FTOFS and Claire's are not alone in
OL,18,Fexperiencing difficulties," the firm
OL,19,Fsaid.
