OL,3,CClaire's and The Original Factory Shop
OL,4,Ccollapse into administration
OL,6,F"A combination of very weak consumer
OL,7,Fconfidence, highly adverse government
OL,8,Ffiscal policies, and continued cost
OL,9,Finflation is causing many established
OL,10,Fand much-loved businesses to suffer
OL,11,Fbadly.
OL,13,F"It's a simple fact that if retailers
OL,14,Fcan't make money, they risk having to
OL,15,Fclose, and jobs across the country are
OL,16,Flost."
OL,18,FModella bought more than 150 Claire's
OL,19,Fshops last year, but 145 were not
OL,20,Fincluded in the deal, leading to their
OL,21,Fclosure.
