OL,4,Ccollapse into administration
OL,6,FThe fashion accessories chain had
OL,7,Fappointed administrators for its UK
OL,8,Fand Ireland business after filing for
OL,9,Fbankruptcy in the US.
OL,11,FTOFS, a discount department store
OL,12,Fchain, was sold to the investment firm
OL,13,Fin February.
OL,15,FModella has become a significant force
OL,16,Fin the British retail industry, having
OL,17,Fbought WH Smith's high street chain
OL,18,Flast year and taking over arts and
OL,19,Fcrafts retailer Hobbycraft in 2024.
